{"tid":1394974,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"行政長官梁振英簽署保普選反佔中的表格","createTime":"2019-08-01T15:07:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T15:10:14.000Z","uid":45706,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"351e8cdecd3375b61c7516745479fee863a950d5","tid":1394974,"uid":45706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:07:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=109652&amp;refer=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D109652%26refer%3D&d=BmTzKXBjX6ru83xd6aIIEUzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=7fa51177\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D109652%26refer%3D&h=ccfb1a7c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=109652&amp;refer=</a><br />\n<br />\n【now新聞台】行政長官梁振英簽署保普選反佔中的表格。<br />\n<br />\n保普選反佔中數名發起人到香港總商會辦事處簽署反佔中表格。梁振英在表格上簽名，並填上個人資料，他其後交出身分證予工作人員核對身分。<br />\n梁振英今次簽名，特首辦主任邱騰華和政府新聞處官員亦有隨行。<span style=\"color: red;\">但梁振英強調，是以社會一分子的身分參與簽署</span>，有其他官員隨行是因為要向傳媒發放其他消息。"},{"pid":"4e088a2bdc0b3d762f32d9eacaacc97d2bd8f5be","tid":1394974,"uid":251292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:10:14.000Z","msg":"唔講都唔記得呢件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又一個point反駁"}]}